name: Integration TeamSpace
description:
The TeamSpace [Integration TeamSpace] has been created.

You can forward the TeamSpace user credentials for that user to edit, or you can do the following:
 -  Log in to API Creator as this TeamSpace user, select Your TeamSpace from the gear icon menu, select the user from the TeamSpace Users list, and then edit the password.
 -  Open the CA Live API Creator Admin API (Admin API), in the Manage section, click Users, select the TeamSpace user, and then edit the password.
